name: Hatched Forms X(COPY)
description:
A tribute to XCOPY's 'Right-click and Save As guy', released into the public domain on 22 Jan 2022.

Part of a study of creating a simulated plotted ink on paper look through an algorithm which generates hatched lines within custom polygons.

2000 × 2000 GIF, 8 frames
Made in p5js
Created 24 Jan 22

Artist: @Yazid
